text: Wiltuniam ninhinga westmerc ðaræ hina land to scaerege norðmearc East Leanaham eastmearc Cyningessnade to feferesham suðmearc & his teares les on Cyninges dune to teninge faledun & his ceares les, to Beringtune on Cyninges firhðe suue to ðeon lond belimpe.
And widunga on Cyningessnade suue to ðiam londe belimpe.
Ðis sind ða daen hæra ðes londes ninsila herst rusting den ðorn den, on mapol der hest ðrio den friððingden twa on friðesleasIIIIon tun laf hirste in on haðdune suðan an be suðan stan ea an.
